to%20do%20with%20a%20product's%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDhanji%20Prasanna%20said%20engineers%20should%20focus%20on%20purpose%2C%20not%20perfect%20syntax%20or%20architecture.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20comments%20come%20as%20tech%20leaders%20continue%20to%20emphasize%20the%20importance%20of%20coding%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20engineering%20circles%2C%20clean%2C%20elegant%20code%20is%20the%20gold%20standard%2C%20but%20Block's%20chief%20technology%20officer%20said%20that's%20overrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDhanji%20Prasanna%2C%20the%20fintech%20company's%20technology%20lead%2C%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLenny's%20Podcast%26quot%3B%20published%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20engineers%20think%20that%20code%20quality%20is%20important%20to%20building%20a%20successful%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bthe%20two%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerfect%20code%20doesn't%20make%20a%20great%20product%2C%20solving%20real%20problems%20does%2C%20said%20Prasanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrasanna%20said%20he%20learned%20that%20when%20he%20was%20at%20Google.%20When%20the%20company%20bought%20YouTube%20in%202006%2C%20Google's%20engineers%20were%20horrified%20by%20the%20video%20site's%20codebases%20and%20%26quot%3Bhow%20terrible%20their%20architecture%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20YouTube%2C%20not%20Google's%20Google%20Video%2C%20became%20one%20of%20the%20most%20successful%20products%20in%20the%20company's%20history%2C%20Prasanna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20has%20very%20little%20to%20do%20with%20how%20well%20it%20was%20architected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20real%20measure%20of%20the%20product's%20success%20is%20whether%20it%20actually%20serves%20users%20and%20solves%20a%20problem%20for%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20focus%20on%20what%20we're%20trying%20to%20build%20and%20whom%20we're%20trying%20to%20build%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%2