i-tariff%20ad%2C%20featuring%20quotes%20from%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20that%20other%20than%20to%20sway%20public%20opinion%3F%26quot%3B%20Bessent%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20said%20he%20had%20paused%20trade%20talks%20with%20Canada%20and%20would%20impose%20a%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20its%20goods%20because%20of%20the%20ad.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Treasury%20Secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-wall-street-treasury-secretary-donald-trump-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScott%20Bessent%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Canada's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-reagan-ad-led-trump-to-end-canada-trade-talks-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanti-tariff%20ad%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20featuring%20former%20US%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B%20and%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bpsy-ops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20on%20CNBC%2C%20Bessent%20answered%20a%20question%20about%20why%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-canada-reagan-ad-airs-world-series-game-two-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esetting%20trade%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20a%20television%20ad%20he%20didn't%20like.%20The%20ad%2C%20released%20on%20October%2016%2C%20contained%20a%20voiceover%20of%20Reagan's%201987%20address%20in%20defence%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20propaganda%20against%20US%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Bessent%20said%20to%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20psy-ops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20the%20government%20of%20Ontario%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20told%20that%20they%20have%20spent%2C%20or%20were%20planning%20to%20spend%2C%20up%20to%20%2475%20million%20on%20these%20ads%20to%20come%20across%20the%20US%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20that%20other%20than%20to%20sway%20public%20opinion%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBessent%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Asia%20with%20Trump%20inking%20trade%20deals%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20ad%20had%20been%20taken%20down.%20But%20he%20said%20putting%20the%20ad%20up%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bterrible%2C%20terrible%20judgment%26quot%3B%20by%20Ontario's%20premier%2C%20Doug%20Ford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20Sunday%20%26quot%3BFace%20the%20Nation%26quot%3B%20interview%20with%20CBS's%20Margaret%20Brennan%2C%20Bessent%20made%20a%20similar%20statement%2C%20calling%20the%20ad%20an%20%26quot%3Binterference%20in%20US%20sovereign%20matters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clearly%20damaged%20our%20relationship%20with%20the%20most%20populous%20province%20in%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Brennan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20US%20Treasury%20and%20the%20Ontario%20Premier's%20Office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277c502e4-8373-4b23-bc78-3584e97888dd%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20ad%20backlash%20unfolded%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20province%20of%20Ontario's%20minute-long%20ad%20included%20a%20voiceover%20of%20Reagan's%201987%20%26quot%3BRadio%20Address%20to%20the%20Nation%20on%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Trade.%26quot%3B%20The%20address%20said%20that%20while%20tariffs%20may%20seem%20%26quot%3Bpatriotic%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20eventually%20%26quot%3Bhurt%20every%20American%20worker%20and%20consumer%26quot%3B%20and%20lead%20to%20retaliation%20and%20trade%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ronald%20Reagan%20Presidential%20Foundation%20and%20Institute%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Ontario%20had%20misrepresented%20Reagan's%20comments%2C%20and%20the%20province%20had%20not%20sought%20the%20foundation's%20permission%20to%20use%20or%20edit%20the%20former%20president's%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20slammed%20Ontario's%20ad%20in%20a%20Friday%20Truth%20Social%20post%2C%20saying%20he%20would%20end%20trade%20negotiations%20with%20Canada%20over%20the%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOntario's%20premier%2C%20Ford%2C%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20X%20post%20that%20his%20intention%20with%20the%20ad%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Binitiate%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20economy%20that%20Americans%20want%20to%20build%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs%20on%20workers%20and%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20achieved%20our%20goal%2C%20having%20reached%20US%20audiences%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20directed%20my%20team%20to%20keep%20putting%20our%20message%20in%20front%20of%20Americans%20over%20the%20weekend%20so%20that%20we%20can%20air%20our%20commercial%20during%20the%20first%20two%20World%20Series%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ford%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20with%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Mark%20Carney%20and%20decided%20to%20pause%20the%20ad%20from%20Monday%20so%20trade%20talks%20could%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%20was%20aired%20during%20the%20World%20Series%20games%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20Saturday%20Truth%20Social%20post%20that%20he%20would%20impose%20an%20additional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-canada-tariffs-ronald-reagan-ad-ontario-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E10%25%20tariff%20on%20Canadian%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20above%20the%20current%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20on%20Canadian%20goods%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20United%20States-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%20were%20taxed%20at%2035%25%20before%20the%20proposed%2010%25%20hike.%20Trump%20has%20also%20imposed%20separate%20tariffs%20on%20products%20like%20automobile%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-bessent-canada-re