d.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Ford%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-ford-ceo-mark-fields-automaker-invest-ev-consumer-demand-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Fields%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20demand%20for%20EVs%20in%20the%20US%20will%20slowly%20pick%20up%20again%20after%20the%20Trump%20administration%20axed%20federal%20EV%20incentives%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%2C%20obviously%2C%20a%20pullback%20given%20that%20the%20federal%20incentives%20have%20come%20off%2C%20but%20I%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20gradual%20growth%20in%20the%20EV%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Fields%2C%2064%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFields%20said%20that%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20consumers%20will%20lean%20toward%20clean%20energy%20vehicles%20instead%20of%20combustion-engine%20vehicles%20because%20%26quot%3Boil%20is%20a%20non-renewable%20resource.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20these%20grow%20over%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20at%20the%20pace%20that%20the%20automakers%20thought%2C%26quot%3B%20Fields%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20you're%20seeing%20these%20big%20impairment%20charges%20that%20both%20Ford%20and%20GM%20and%20others%20have%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2014%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeneral-motors-hit-after-rolling-back-its-ev-plans-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Motors%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20exchange%20filing%20that%20it%20was%20taking%20a%20%241.6%20billion%20charge%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20a%20planned%20strategic%20realignment%20of%20our%20EV%20capacity.%26quot%3B%20The%20automaker%20said%20it%20expected%20the%20%26quot%3Badoption%20rate%20of%20EVs%20to%20slow%26quot%3B%20after%20federal%20EV%20incentives%20expired%20on%20September%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20more%20going%20forward%20as%20the%20industry%20adjusts%20to%20a%20new%20demand%20curve%2C%20if%20you%20will%2C%20for%20EVs%2C%26quot%3B%20Fields%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Fields%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20EV%20buyers%20could%20receive%20a%20%247%2C500%20consumer%20tax%20credit%20when%20they%20bought%20a%20new%20EV%20and%20a%20%244%2C000%20credit%20for%20a%20used%20EV.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-tax-credit-end-what-to-know-tesla-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eended%20both%20schemes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFields%20was%20Ford's%20CEO%20from%202014%20to%202017.%20He%20joined%20the%20company%20in%201989%20after%20graduating%20with%20an%20MBA%20from%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%20Before%20becoming%20CEO%2C%20Fields%20held%20various%20senior%20leadership%20positions%20and%20was%20Ford's%20chief%20operating%20officer%20from%202012%20to%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Fields%20said%20US%20automakers%20had%20overestimated%20consumer%20demand%20for%20EVs%20and%20%26quot%3Bwent%20full%20bore%26quot%3B%20into%20making%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20an%20advantage%2C%20at%20least%20they%20thought%20at%20the%20time%2C%20has%20now%20probably%20turned%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20albatross%20as%20the%20market%20take-up%20of%20EVs%20is%20going%20to%20be%20lower%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20near%20to%20medium%20term%2C%20than%20they%20plan%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Fields%20told%20CNBC%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20aired%20on%20October%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Tesla%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ex-global-sales-chief-ev-market-grow-without-subsidies-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJon%20McNeill%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20a%20different%20view%20from%20Fields.%20McNeill%20was%20Tesla's%20president%20for%20global%20sales%20and%20marketing%20from%202015%20to%202018.%20He%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20on%20October%202%20that%20the%20expiry%20of%20federal%20EV%20incentives%20won't%20slow%20down%20the%20US%20EV%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Europe%2C%20France%20and%20Germany%20in%20particular%20rolled%20subsidies%20off%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20what%20happened%20after%20that%2C%20surprisingly%2C%20was%20the%20market%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20McNeill%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market's%20established%2C%20and%20we're%20probably%20ready%20to%20have%20a%20market%20that%20can%20grow%20without%20subsidies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20current%20CEO%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-china-completely-dominating-tesla-gm-ford-ev-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJim%20Farley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20at%20a%20conference%20in%20Detroit%20on%20September%2030%20that%20the%20pullback%20on%20federal%20EV%20incentives%20could%20halve%20US%20EV%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20near%20term%2C%20I%20believe%20EV%20adoption%20will%20now%20only%20be%20about%205%25%20of%20the%20US%20market%2C%20but%20this%20is%20going%20to%20grow%2C%20especially%20for%20affordable%20EV%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20on%20October%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20shares%20are%20up%20nearly%2040%25%20year%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-ford-ceo-ev-market-gradual-growth-pullback-federal-incentives-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1761538404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68feccf2c007ca8c2737a73d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-ford-ceo-ev-market-gradual-grow