0Jinping.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20Navy%20F%2FA-18F%20Super%20Hornet%20and%20an%20MH-60R%20Sea%20Hawk%20helicopter%20crashed%20in%20separate%20incidents%20on%20Sunday%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20the%20US%20Pacific%20Fleet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20military%20aircraft%20had%20been%20deployed%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-jet-fuel-traces-uss-nimitz-sailor-says-worse-problem-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUSS%20Nimitz%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20went%20down%2030%20minutes%20apart%20from%20each%20other%20during%20routine%20operations%2C%20the%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20personnel%20involved%20are%20safe%20and%20in%20stable%20condition.%20The%20cause%20of%20both%20incidents%20is%20currently%20under%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20the%20Sea%20Hawk%20was%20the%20first%20to%20go%20down%20at%20about%202.45%20p.m.%20local%20time.%20It%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BBattle%20Cats%26quot%3B%20of%20Helicopter%20Maritime%20Strike%20Squadron%2073.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20crew%20members%20on%20board%20were%20later%20rescued%2C%20the%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Super%20Hornet%2C%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BFighting%20Redcocks%26quot%3B%20of%20Strike%20Fighter%20Squadron%2022%2C%20crashed%20at%203%3A15%20p.m.%2C%20per%20the%20Navy.%20The%20statement%20added%20that%20both%20crew%20members%20had%20ejected%20just%20before%20the%20fighter%20jet%20went%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20separate%20incidents%20come%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20engages%20in%20a%20diplomatic%20tour%20in%20Asia%20this%20week%2C%20which%20he%20kick-started%20with%20a%20meeting%20in%20Malaysia%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tour%20is%20expected%20to%20include%20a%20leg%20in%20China%2C%20where%20Trump%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20China's%20leader%2C%20Xi%20Jinping.%20Trade%20is%20high%20on%20the%20agenda%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20threatens%20severe%20tariffs%20on%20China%20and%20tensions%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20continue%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETreasury%20Secretary%20Scott%20Bessent%20suggested%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20US%20may%20hold%20back%20on%20plans%20to%20impose%20100%25%20tariffs%20on%20China%20after%20Trump's%20preliminary%20talks%20with%20Beijing%20officials%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Sunday's%20fighter%20crash%20marks%20the%20US%20Navy's%20fourth%20Super%20Hornet%20loss%20in%20the%20last%2012%20months.%20The%20first%20of%20the%20%2460%20million%20fighters%20was%20shot%20down%20last%20December%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-fighter-jet-downing-another-red-sea-friendly-fire-incident-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efriendly%20fire%20over%20the%20Red%20Sea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20another%20two%20fell%20off%20their%20flight%20deck%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20previously%20lost%20aircraft%20had%20been%20deployed%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-aircraft-carrier-red-sea-lost-another-super-hornet-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUSS%20Harry%20S.%20Truman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20in%20the%20same%20class%20as%20the%20Nimitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MH-60R%20Sea%20Hawk%20is%20the%20Navy's%20most%20advanced%20variant%20of%20the%20Sea%20Hawk%2C%20which%20is%20essentially%20a%20sea-based%20version%20of%20the%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter.%20Estimated%20to%20cost%20about%20%2440%20million%2C%20it's%20built%20for%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20missions%2C%20including%20finding%20and%20attacking%20submarines%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20flying%20command%20post%2C%20or%20conducting%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nimitz%2C%20commissioned%20in%201975%2C%20is%20the%20Navy's%20oldest%20aircraft%20carrier%20in%20service%20and%20is%20the%20lead%20ship%20of%20its%20class.%20The