onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-vietnam-work-affordable-not-returning-america-da-nang-2025-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20EV%20market%20suffers%20from%20the%20'brutal%20competition'%20of%20too%20many%20entrepreneurs%20and%20engineers%2C%20says%20top%20China%20watcher%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225112%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Wang%20is%20wearing%20a%20blue%20jacket%20and%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20his%20shelves.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d4daac57d362d375e8d183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223834%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20in%20China%20is%20cut-throat%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20for%20that%20situation%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Wang%2C%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%3A%20China's%20Quest%20to%20Engineer%20the%20Future%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3Cp%3EDan%20Wang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDan%20Wang%20lived%20in%20China%20from%202017%20to%202023%20while%20covering%20the%20country%20as%20a%20technology%20analyst.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20published%20his%20first%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%3A%20China's%20Quest%20to%20Engineer%20the%20Future%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20August.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWang%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20China's%20industrial%20successes%20were%20driven%20by%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20EV%20market%20is%20saturated%20with%20way%20too%20many%20car%20company%20founders%20who%20are%20deadlocked%20in%20a%20brutal%20battle%20for%20market%20share%2C%20says%20China%20analyst%20Dan%20Wang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20lived%20in%20China%20from%202017%20to%202023%2C%20where%20he%20covered%20the%20country%20as%20a%20technology%20analyst%20for%20Gavekal%20Dragonomics%2C%20a%20financial%20services%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20Stanford%20University's%20Hoover%20Institution.%20Wang%20published%20his%20first%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%3A%20China's%20Quest%20to%20Engineer%20the%20Future%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20the%20EV%20price%20war%20in%20the%20country%20won't%20stop%20anytime%20soon%2C%20and%20that's%20by%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20too%20many%20entrepreneurs%2C%20too%20many%20engineers%2C%20and%20too%20much%20desire%20for%20local%20governments%20to%20support%20local%20champions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrutal%20competition%20has%20produced%20many%20of%20China's%20successes%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20solar%20and%20electric%20vehicles.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20reason%20for%20many%20of%20these%20industries%20to%20have%20low%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20wrote%20in%20%26quot%3BBreakneck%26quot%3B%20that%20government%20support%20was%20a%20key%20reason%20Chinese%20tech%20giants%20like%20Huawei%20and%20Xiaomi%20ventured%20into%20the%20automotive%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20sort%20of%20expansion%20is%20driven%20both%20by%20the%20fiercely%20competitive%20market%20environments%20and%20by%20government%20subsidies%20that%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20companies%20to%20try%20their%20hand%20at%20making%20new%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20allow%20companies%20to%20unleash%20a%20flood%20of%20undifferentiated%20products%2C%20ruthlessly%20underbid%20each%20other%2C%20and%20pray%20their%20competitors%20run%20out%20of%20money%20before%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20race%20to%20the%20bottom%20is%20starting%20to%20show%20up%20in%20EV%20companies'%20bottom%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20BYD%20said%20its%20net%20profit%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20fell%20by%2030%25%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBYD%20said%20in%20its%20earnings%20report%20that%20%26quot%3Bshort-term%20profitability%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20pulled%20down%20by%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-share-price-slumps-analysts-gravy-train-slowing-chinese-ev-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20discounting.%20In%20May%2C%20BYD%20said%20it%20was%20slashing%20prices%20on%2022%20electric%20and%20hybrid%20models%20until%20the%20end%20of%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20in%20China%20is%20cutthroat%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20for%20that%20situation%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20partly%20a%20function%20of%20the%20giant%20scale%20of%20China's%20market%2C%20in%20which%20entrepreneurs%20are%20always%20daring%20to%20pursue%20opportunities%2C%20which%20is%20a%20feature%20of%20China's%20highly%20dynamic%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b375e34c-42fe-40e5-b47d-911b5b6c7b0f%5C%22%3EHundreds%20of%20billions%20in%20subsidies%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20US's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECenter%20for%20Strategic%20%26amp%3B%20International%20Studies%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-electric-vehicles-government-subsidies-win-ev-race-byd-tesla-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China's%20government%20had%20spent%20at%20least%20%24230%20billion%20since%202009%20supporting%20local%20EV%20champions%20such%20as%20BYD.%20The%20think%20tank%20said%20the%20figure%20was%20probably%20an%20underestimate%2C%20since%20it%20did%20not%20include%20incentives%20and%20subsidies%20from%20regional%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivian%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frivian-ceo-china-evs-low-cost-competition-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERJ%20Scaringe%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20the%20%26quot%3BEverything%20Electric%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20an%2